HEAT
CONDUCTION
THROUGH
A
POLYATOMIC
GAS
A
HEAT
CONDUCTION
PROBLEM
IS
SET
UP
WHICH
IN
ESSENCE
SIMULATES
THE
CONDITIONS
ARISING
WHEN
A
PLANE
SHOCK
